Date: 1992-06-29

Title: Maurer-Cartan forms and equations for two-dimensional

superdiffeomorphismsAuthors: Francois Gieres

Comments: (LATEX, 8 pages), MPI-Ph/92-43

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 34 (1993) 836-843

We present explicit expressions for the Maurer-Cartan forms of thesuperdiffeomorphism group associated to a super Riemann surface. As anapplication to superconformal field theory, we use these forms to evaluate theeffective action for the factorized superdiffeomorphism anomaly.